</div>
<div class="note success"><h4 id="Welcome-to-my-website"><a href="#Welcome-to-my-website" class="headerlink" title="Welcome to my website!"></a>Welcome to my website!</h4><p>This platform will showcases my professional experience, also sharing snippets of my personal life.</p>
</div>  

<div class="note info"><h4 id="Reminder"><a href="#Reminder" class="headerlink" title="Reminder"></a>Reminder</h4><p>網站長期維護中~<br>网站长期维护中~<br>Website under long-term maintenance~</p>
</div>

<div class="tabs" id="first-unique-name"><ul class="nav-tabs"><li class="tab active"><a href="#first-unique-name-1">網站使用指引</a></li><li class="tab"><a href="#first-unique-name-2">网站使用指引</a></li><li class="tab"><a href="#first-unique-name-3">Website Guidelines</a></li></ul><div class="tab-content"><div class="tab-pane active" id="first-unique-name-1"><p><strong>電腦使用者</strong></p>
