<p><strong>移动设备用户</strong></p>
<div class="note "><p>移动设备的主菜单在网页顶部；作者栏目和目录则在左下角</p>
</div></div><div class="tab-pane" id="first-unique-name-3"><p><strong>Desktop Users</strong></p>
<div class="note "><p>The 🌗 at bottom right corner allows you to switch between light and dark mode<br>The website’s default language is <mark class="label primary">Traditional-Hong Kong</mark>. You can switch languages at the bottom of the page (Traditional-Hong Kong&#x2F;Simplified&#x2F;English).<br>After switching languages, the homepage will display articles in the corresponding language:<br>–&gt;<a href="https://wingsze.us.kg/en/Personal%20Resume/">Personal Resume</a><br>–&gt;<a href="https://wingsze.us.kg/en/Personal%20Portfolio/">Personal Portfolio</a></p>
<p><mark class="label success">Left-side Features</mark></p>
<div class="tabs" id="fourth-unique-name"><ul class="nav-tabs"><li class="tab active"><a href="#fourth-unique-name-1">Menu</a></li><li class="tab"><a href="#fourth-unique-name-2">Author's Column</a></li><li class="tab"><a href="#fourth-unique-name-3">Table of Contents</a></li></ul><div class="tab-content"><div class="tab-pane active" id="fourth-unique-name-1"><p>Home(Welcome again!), About (Multilingual Self-introduction),<br>Categories (Multilingual versions of articles), Search(Enter a keyword to search for related content)</p></div><div class="tab-pane" id="fourth-unique-name-2"><p>Includes email address and personal homepages on other platforms, feel free to contact for more information!</p></div><div class="tab-pane" id="fourth-unique-name-3"><p>Appears on the left side after entering an article</p></div></div></div></div>

<p><strong>Mobile Device Users</strong></p>
<div class="note "><p>The main menu for mobile devices is at the top of the web page; the author’s column and table of contents are located at the bottom left.</p>
</div></div></div></div>]]></content>
